# Lendsqr FE assessment runs zero-config out of the box.
# This file exists so contributors know which environment variables
# are read (currently none beyond Vercel-injected URLs).

# Optional: mocky.io payload URL if you want to swap the local API
# route for a hosted JSON payload. Not consumed in the current
# implementation, but referenced in README's "Design decisions".
# NEXT_PUBLIC_USERS_API_URL=
